trans-unit.source: Animates the value of a <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Point3D"></xref> property using linear interpolation between two values.
trans-unit.target: Animerer verdien for en <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Point3D"> </xref> egenskap ved hjelp av Lineær interpolering mellom to verdier.

trans-unit.source: An animation updates the value of a property over a period of time.
trans-unit.target: En animasjon oppdaterer verdien for en egenskap over en viss tid.

trans-unit.source: An animation effect can be subtle, such as moving a <xref:System.Windows.Shapes.Shape> a few pixels left and right, or dramatic, such as enlarging an object to 200 times its original size while spinning it and changing its color.
trans-unit.target: En animasjonseffekt kan være svak, for eksempel flytting av en <xref:System.Windows.Shapes.Shape>noen piksler venstre og høyre eller store, for eksempel blir større objektets 200 ganger den opprinnelige størrelsen under starter den og endre fargene.</xref:System.Windows.Shapes.Shape>

trans-unit.source: To create an animation in [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winclient](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], you associate an animation with an object's property value.
trans-unit.target: Opprette en animasjon i [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winclient](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], du knytte en animasjon til et objekt egenskapsverdi.

trans-unit.source: Target Values The Point3DAnimation class creates a transition between two target values.
trans-unit.target: Verdier for Point3DAnimation målklassen oppretter en overgang mellom to målverdier.

trans-unit.source: To set its target values, use its <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Point3DAnimation.From%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Point3DAnimation.To%2A>, and <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Point3DAnimation.By%2A> properties.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil angi målverdiene, kan du bruke den <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Point3DAnimation.From%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Point3DAnimation.To%2A>, og <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Point3DAnimation.By%2A>Egenskaper.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Point3DAnimation.By%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Point3DAnimation.To%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Point3DAnimation.From%2A>

trans-unit.source: Freezable Features Because the Point3DAnimation class inherits from <xref:System.Windows.Freezable>, Point3DAnimation objects gain several special features, which include the following: they can be declared as , shared among multiple objects, made read-only to improve performance, cloned, and made thread-safe.

trans-unit.source: For more information about the different features provided by <xref:System.Windows.Freezable> objects, see the [Freezable Objects Overview](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that specifies whether the animation's value accumulates when it repeats.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om den animasjonen verdien akkumulerer når den gjentas.

trans-unit.source: When this property is set to **true**, the animation's output values only accumulate when the animation's <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.RepeatBehavior%2A> property causes it to repeat its simple duration.
trans-unit.target: Når denne egenskapen er satt til **true**, animasjonen malens utdatanavn verdier samler bare når animasjonen <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.RepeatBehavior%2A>egenskapen gjør at den skal repeteres varigheten enkle.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.RepeatBehavior%2A>

trans-unit.source: It does not accumulate its values when it restarts because its parent repeated or because its clock was restarted from a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ClockController.Begin%2A> call.
trans-unit.target: Det ikke samles opp verdiene når den startes på nytt fordi overordnet gjentatt eller fordi klokken ble startet på nytt fra en <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ClockController.Begin%2A>kall.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ClockController.Begin%2A>
